## School Admin Approval Flow (Platform Admin)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A[Platform Admin Logged In] --> B[Navigate to /admin/school-admin-applications]
    B --> C[GET /api/admin/school-admin-applications]
    C --> D[Fetch All Applications]

    D --> E{Application Status}
    E -->|pending_approval| F[Show Approve/Reject Buttons]
    E -->|approved| G[Show Approved Badge]
    E -->|rejected| H[Show Rejected Badge]

    F --> I[Click Approve Button]
    I --> J[POST /api/admin/school-admin-applications/:id/approve]

    J --> K[Verify Application Exists]
    K --> L[Update Application Status → approved]
    L --> M[Set reviewedAt & reviewedBy]
    M --> N[Update User Type → school-admin]

    N --> O[Assign school-admin Role<br/>user_roles table]
    O --> P[Link User to School<br/>users.schoolId]

    P --> Q[Success Response]
    Q --> R[Refresh Page - Status: approved]

    style A fill:#e1f5ff
    style K fill:#f8d7da
    style L fill:#d4edda
    style O fill:#d4edda
    style P fill:#d4edda
    style Q fill:#d4edda
    style R fill:#c3e6cb
```

